  "2281820": {
    "name": "精灵化化大冒险",
    "steam_appid": 2281820,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "化化训练师你好，欢迎来到《精灵化化大冒险》的世界。这里集合了爬塔、精灵养成收集、角色扮演、Roguelike等多种元素。培养专属于你的化化军团，然后向着最高层进发吧！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2281820/extras/dce6b8f1d105b904b21e5ec52888701f.webp?t=1770300076\" width=610 height=60 /></span><br><br>每局开始，都会有三只可爱（或者说...奇怪）的化化等着你领走它。选择一只！然后开始你的爬塔之旅！在冒险过程中，你将不断遇到新的化化，也能捕捉那些对你有恶意的化化。它们的属性、能力、技能和样貌都各不相同，请训练师根据想要游玩的风格仔细挑选，进行培养，最终组建强力的化化军团吧！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2281820/extras/ceae489b83a15ca0f39576e4506d0a6f.poster.avif?t=1770300076\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2281820/extras/ceae489b83a15ca0f39576e4506d0a6f.webm?t=1770300076\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2281820/extras/ceae489b83a15ca0f39576e4506d0a6f.mp4?t=1770300076\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>小提示：培养你的化化时别忘了，适当加入一些爱。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2281820/extras/51d56521fe16eab6336f9a896a2557bb.webp?t=1770300076\" width=610 height=60 /></span><br><br>对了训练师，化化们分为空间、糖果、黏黏、鬼魂（？）等多种不同的属性，而它们也有自己独特的升级路线，相同属性的化化可获得专属的能力加成，不同属性的化化聚在一起也能产生奇妙的化学反应。当你尝试将三只相同或不同的化化之间进行融合时，砰！一只完全不同且更强力的化化就诞生了！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2281820/extras/687dfd8ce915b140bbac342567a70368.poster.avif?t=1770300076\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2281820/extras/687dfd8ce915b140bbac342567a70368.webm?t=1770300076\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2281820/extras/687dfd8ce915b140bbac342567a70368.mp4?t=1770300076\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>所以，请大胆去尝试，化化们能诞生出无限种可能，去让它们升级、进化、融合吧！你的阵容会因此充满惊喜，或者...惊吓。但嘿！它们可是可爱的化化呀！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2281820/extras/8fb3f01b752c5eaa4125639cacae27e4.webp?t=1770300076\" width=610 height=60 /></span><br><br>《精灵化化大冒险》的世界主题各不相同，过程中你可以选择自己的路线，遭遇稀奇古怪的敌人和Boss，运营自己的化化军团，搭配不同的属性和能力将它们逐一击破吧！对了，途中你还会遇到各种随机事件，你的爬塔之旅会因为这些有趣的事件充满变数，并且每一轮都能获得全新的体验。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2281820/extras/03e9c05231de7f5a52987cc3c39b18a6.poster.avif?t=1770300076\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2281820/extras/03e9c05231de7f5a52987cc3c39b18a6.webm?t=1770300076\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2281820/extras/03e9c05231de7f5a52987cc3c39b18a6.mp4?t=1770300076\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>差点忘了一件重要的事！可爱的化化们不舍得让你产生很强的挫败感。每当你开启新一轮冒险，都能看到来自上一局的遗产，带着它们能让你的爬塔之旅更加顺利。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2281820/extras/ef5d71b5549d4d250c78b52547b33699.poster.avif?t=1770300076\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2281820/extras/ef5d71b5549d4d250c78b52547b33699.webm?t=1770300076\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2281820/extras/ef5d71b5549d4d250c78b52547b33699.mp4?t=1770300076\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2281820/extras/4baf17e0564df7317b321e8566a24546.webp?t=1770300076\" width=610 height=60 /></span><br><br>我刚刚粗略的算了一下，《精灵化化大冒险》的世界中的化化数量，多达近百种！（什么时候这么多的）<br><br>而《化化百科》会仔细记录你所遇到的每一个化化，供你研究。有闪亮的化化，有超闪的化化，还有大家都想要的彩虹化化。细心阅读他们的百科条目，探索隐秘的特点和能力，真正掌握这些生物的特质！这些磨人的小可爱，你都能抓到吗？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2281820/extras/2f8a2fd978c0a08540d086a24a811d40.poster.avif?t=1770300076\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2281820/extras/2f8a2fd978c0a08540d086a24a811d40.webm?t=1770300076\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2281820/extras/2f8a2fd978c0a08540d086a24a811d40.mp4?t=1770300076\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
